description: Lists all inference events that have been found for the specified inference scheduler.

parameters.name: InferenceSchedulerName
parameters.description: The name of the inference scheduler for the inference events listed.

parameters.name: IntervalStartTime
parameters.description: Lookout for Equipment will return all the inference events with an end time equal to or greater than the start time given.

parameters.name: IntervalEndTime
parameters.description: Returns all the inference events with an end start time equal to or greater than less than the end time given.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: An opaque pagination token indicating where to continue the listing of inference executions.

nested_items.name: InferenceEventSummaries
nested_items.description: Provides an array of information about the individual inference events returned from the ListInferenceEvents operation, including scheduler used, event start time, event end time, diagnostics, and so on.

nested_items.name: InferenceSchedulerArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the inference scheduler being used for the inference event.

nested_items.name: InferenceSchedulerName
nested_items.description: The name of the inference scheduler being used for the inference events.

nested_items.name: EventStartTime
nested_items.description: Indicates the starting time of an inference event.

nested_items.name: EventEndTime
nested_items.description: Indicates the ending time of an inference event.

nested_items.name: Diagnostics
nested_items.description: An array which specifies the names and values of all sensors contributing to an inference event.

nested_items.name: EventDurationInSeconds
nested_items.description: Indicates the size of an inference event in seconds.
